Gift version 0.03
=================

INSTALLATION

To install this module first install the
Parse::Yapp module. 
You can do it as administrator using the following command:

perl -MCPAN -e install Parse::Yapp

Next:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires Parse::Yapp


